60|$|Hardly {{the type}} of man for a hero! And yet I do not know. Perhaps he fought harder than many a man who conquers. In the world's courts, we are {{compelled}} to judge on circumstantial evidence only, and the <b>chief</b> <b>witness,</b> the man's soul, cannot very well be called.|$|E
